Pre-Game Insights: Travis Head: 'Australia have to win this game to remain alive for the semi-finals.'
Post-Match Reflections: Rohit Sharma: 'Milestones do not matter: Rohit', 'We don't want to do anything different, play the same way and understand what each person has to do.'
Mitch Marsh: 'Disappointing. It happens in the game of cricket. In the course of 40 overs, there are a lot of small margins. India were the better team, Rohit is a class player.'
Miscellaneous Highlights: India will now meet England in the semi-final of the tournament.
Others: India reach the semi-final of the T20 World Cup 2024 undefeated.
India defeat Australia in their final Super 8 match in St Lucia on Monday, 24 June at St Lucia.
